snippet.title: Playtest Announcement - Red Metal
snippet.description:
Playtest Red Metal now on @GameRoundCo !
Take part in shaping the game by giving your valuable feedback.
Download the demo from https://gameround.co/detail/485/info and play until 22nd May.

Wishlist on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2741160/Red_Metal/
